branchCategory.name: NC(D)Q2WB-Z, Compact Cylinder, Double Acting Double Rod, Large Bore (125-160)
branchCategory.description: Standard large bore single acting, double rod version of the NCQ2 compact cylinder. The large bore NCQ2 is available in bore sizes from 125mm to 160mm. It comes standard with male or female piston rod threads. For mounting flexibility, it is possible to mount auto switches on any of the 4 surfaces.
